{"session_id": "20260315_134635_f8b8c282", "turn_index": 1, "timestamp": "2026-03-15T13:50:47.522532+00:00", "player_text": "你好", "npc_id": "npc_002", "location_id": "loc_001", "model_used": "qwen3-max-2026-01-23", "output": {"narration": "晨露村的草堆旁，信使托比正紧张地整理着背上的信袋，一见到你便露出略显局促的笑容。", "npc_dialogue": [{"npc_id": "npc_002", "text": "啊！你好你好！我是托比，村里的信使。你……你看起来不像坏人，对吧？最近村子里可不太平，恶龙都把人抓走了！"}], "world_updates": {"player_location": null, "npc_moves": [], "flags_delta": {}, "quest_updates": {}, "quest_progress_updates": [], "inventory_delta": {}, "npc_personality_updates": []}, "memory_summary": "玩家首次与信使托比对话，托比自我介绍并提及恶龙事件。", "safety": {"refuse": false, "reason": null}}, "move_rejections": [], "move_refusals": [], "move_applied_count": 0, "move_rejected_count": 0, "move_refused_count": 0, "guard_warnings": [], "rag": {"enabled": true, "always_include_ids": ["20260315_134635_f8b8c282:world_bible:-:-:-:-:801c6423", "20260315_134635_f8b8c282:location:-:loc_001:-:-:0586f9cb", "20260315_134635_f8b8c282:npc_profile:npc_002:-:-:-:501e7337"], "retrieved_ids": [], "retrieval_backend": "persistent_hybrid", "embedding_backend": "hashing", "vectorstore_path": "data/vectorstore/20260315_134635_f8b8c282", "filters": [{"session_id": "20260315_134635_f8b8c282", "npc_id": "npc_002", "doc_type": ["memory", "summary", "lore"]}, {"session_id": "20260315_134635_f8b8c282", "location_id": "loc_001", "doc_type": ["memory", "summary", "lore"]}, {"session_id": "20260315_134635_f8b8c282", "doc_type": ["memory", "summary", "lore"]}], "counts": {"always_include": 3, "retrieved": 0, "store_total": 16}}}
{"session_id": "20260315_134635_f8b8c282", "turn_index": 2, "timestamp": "2026-03-15T13:51:08.269377+00:00", "player_text": "对", "npc_id": "npc_002", "location_id": "loc_001", "model_used": "qwen3-max-2026-01-23", "output": {"narration": "托比搓了搓手，紧张地朝村口张望了一眼。", "npc_dialogue": [{"npc_id": "npc_002", "text": "太好了！你真是个好人！我正愁没人陪我去铁砧镇送信呢……那条路最近不太平，听说有哥布林出没。你要是顺路的话，能不能……能不能和我一起走一段？"}], "world_updates": {"player_location": null, "npc_moves": [], "flags_delta": {}, "quest_updates": {}, "quest_progress_updates": [], "inventory_delta": {}, "npc_personality_updates": []}, "memory_summary": "托比请求玩家陪同前往铁砧镇，因害怕路上的危险。", "safety": {"refuse": false, "reason": null}}, "move_rejections": [], "move_refusals": [], "move_applied_count": 0, "move_rejected_count": 0, "move_refused_count": 0, "guard_warnings": [], "rag": {"enabled": true, "always_include_ids": ["20260315_134635_f8b8c282:world_bible:-:-:-:-:801c6423", "20260315_134635_f8b8c282:location:-:loc_001:-:-:0586f9cb", "20260315_134635_f8b8c282:npc_profile:npc_002:-:-:-:501e7337", "20260315_134635_f8b8c282:memory:npc_002:loc_001:1:-:76b0d1f9", "20260315_134635_f8b8c282:summary:-:-:1:-:bddc8d2c"], "retrieved_ids": [], "retrieval_backend": "persistent_hybrid", "embedding_backend": "hashing", "vectorstore_path": "data/vectorstore/20260315_134635_f8b8c282", "filters": [{"session_id": "20260315_134635_f8b8c282", "npc_id": "npc_002", "doc_type": ["memory", "summary", "lore"]}, {"session_id": "20260315_134635_f8b8c282", "location_id": "loc_001", "doc_type": ["memory", "summary", "lore"]}, {"session_id": "20260315_134635_f8b8c282", "doc_type": ["memory", "summary", "lore"]}], "counts": {"always_include": 5, "retrieved": 0, "store_total": 17}}}
{"session_id": "20260315_134635_f8b8c282", "turn_index": 3, "timestamp": "2026-03-15T13:51:52.245392+00:00", "player_text": "可以，我们走吧", "npc_id": "npc_002", "location_id": "loc_001", "model_used": "qwen3-max-2026-01-23", "output": {"narration": "托比松了口气，小心翼翼地背上信袋，朝村口方向迈了一小步。", "npc_dialogue": [{"npc_id": "npc_002", "text": "太感谢你了！有你陪着，我胆子就大些了。我们先去铁砧镇，就在村子东边那条路——不过听说路上有哥布林，咱们得小心点……你带武器了吗？"}], "world_updates": {"player_location": null, "npc_moves": [], "flags_delta": {}, "quest_updates": {}, "quest_progress_updates": [], "inventory_delta": {}, "npc_personality_updates": []}, "memory_summary": "玩家同意陪同托比前往铁砧镇，托比表达感激并提醒路上可能有哥布林。", "safety": {"refuse": false, "reason": null}}, "move_rejections": [], "move_refusals": [], "move_applied_count": 0, "move_rejected_count": 0, "move_refused_count": 0, "guard_warnings": [], "rag": {"enabled": true, "always_include_ids": ["20260315_134635_f8b8c282:world_bible:-:-:-:-:801c6423", "20260315_134635_f8b8c282:location:-:loc_001:-:-:0586f9cb", "20260315_134635_f8b8c282:npc_profile:npc_002:-:-:-:501e7337", "20260315_134635_f8b8c282:memory:npc_002:loc_001:1:-:76b0d1f9", "20260315_134635_f8b8c282:memory:npc_002:loc_001:2:-:54e5fb91", "20260315_134635_f8b8c282:summary:-:-:1:-:bddc8d2c", "20260315_134635_f8b8c282:summary:-:-:2:-:a61383be"], "retrieved_ids": [], "retrieval_backend": "persistent_hybrid", "embedding_backend": "hashing", "vectorstore_path": "data/vectorstore/20260315_134635_f8b8c282", "filters": [{"session_id": "20260315_134635_f8b8c282", "npc_id": "npc_002", "doc_type": ["memory", "summary", "lore"]}, {"session_id": "20260315_134635_f8b8c282", "location_id": "loc_001", "doc_type": ["memory", "summary", "lore"]}, {"session_id": "20260315_134635_f8b8c282", "doc_type": ["memory", "summary", "lore"]}], "counts": {"always_include": 7, "retrieved": 0, "store_total": 18}}}
